  <!-- EN: SanQing bell -->
  <RI_RangeWeapon_SanQingBell.label>三清铃</RI_RangeWeapon_SanQingBell.label>
  <!-- EN: Originally a ritual instrument used in sacrificial rites, the SanQing bell was believed to summon divine forces and exorcism. As time passed, its function gradually shifted, eventually evolving into a specialized artifact designed to break defenses.\n\nThe bell’s body is engraved with talisman and fitted with a specially crafted clapper within. When gently shaken, the clapper strikes the talisman patterns, producing an unusual, ordered tone rather than an ordinary chime. This sound wave can be directed toward a target, inducing resonance within its internal structure, progressively destabilizing its equilibrium and causing defensive systems to falter—or even collapse entirely. -->
  <RI_RangeWeapon_SanQingBell.description>三清铃原为祭祀所用的礼器，具备召神遣将，震慑邪祟的作用。随着岁月流转，其用途逐渐变化，最终发展为用于破障的法器。\n\n铃身外刻符咒，内嵌特制铃舌,轻摇之时，铃舌敲击符纹，激起一种特殊的音律。这种音波可定向释放，对目标体内结构产生共振效应，逐步扰乱其稳定状态，使防御体系失衡，乃至崩解。</RI_RangeWeapon_SanQingBell.description>
